---
// No props — always renders Dr. Onyeije's bio
---

<div style="background-color: var(--dwc-card); border: 1px solid var(--dwc-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start;">
  <div style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 72px; height: 72px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: var(--dwc-border); border: 2px solid var(--dwc-cyan); overflow: hidden;">
    <img
      src="/images/author-headshot.jpg"
      alt="Chukwuma Onyeije, MD, FACOG"
      style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%;"
      onerror="this.style.display='none'"
    />
  </div>
  <div>
    <p style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dwc-white); margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">
      Chukwuma Onyeije, MD, FACOG
    </p>
    <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Maternal-Fetal Medicine Specialist</p>
    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--dwc-muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.6;">
      MFM specialist at Atlanta Perinatal Associates. Founder of CodeCraftMD and OpenMFM.org.
      I write about building physician-owned AI tools, clinical software, and the case for doctors who code.
    </p>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/chukwumaonyeije"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--dwc-cyan);"
      >LinkedIn</a>
      <a
        href="https://x.com/chukwumaonyeije"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--dwc-cyan);"
      >X / Twitter</a>
      <a
        href="/about"
        style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--dwc-cyan);"
      >Full Bio</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
